/******************************************************************
DEVELOPMENT (Specifically CSS/LESS at this moment)
******************************************************************/

Note: please don't edit css directly as it will be overwritten if someone runs the grunt commands below.

Learn LESS: http://lesscss.org/

Install Global Requirements (if you haven't already)
npm (www.npmjs.org)
grunt (gruntjs.com/)
grunt cli (gruntjs.com/)

Setup Steps
$ git init
$ npm install
$ grunt

During LESS and JS Editing
$ grunt

Before uploading to server
$ grunt --prod